original: Bjarnegård, Gustaf Birger, komminister, Gökalund, f. 9/5/07 i Kalmar. G. 35 m. lär. Anna-Greta Sjöblom. Barn: Lars-Ingmar f. 36, Viveka 39, Stefan 43, Göran 47. — Stud:ex. i Kalm. 26, teol. fil. ex. i Lund 29, teol. kand. 32, prakt. teol. prov samt prästv. f. Växjö stift 33. Tjg. s. e. o. prästman i Korsberga, Lemnhult, Ljuder o. Norrahammar, kommin. i Söderåkra sed. 37. Stiftsrådets ombud.
translated: Bjarnegård, Gustaf Birger, vicar, Gökalund, b. 9/5/07 in Kalmar. Married in 1935 to teacher Anna-Greta Sjöblom. Children: Lars-Ingmar b. 1936, Viveka b. 1939, Stefan b. 1943, Göran b. 1947. — Completed gymnasium (secondary school) in Kalmar in 1926, theological fil. exam in Lund 1929, theological kand. (licentiate) in 1932, practical theological exam and ordained a minister of Växjö diocese in 1933. Served as assistant and curate in Korsberga, Lemnhult, Ljuder, and Norrahammar, and as a vicar in Söderåkra from 1937. Delegate of the diocesan board of Växjö.
